Nimma hesaru yenu?
What is your name?
Neevu yenu maad tidira?
What are you doing?
Yelli hog beku?
Where do you want to go?
Yelli kelsa maad tidira?
Where are you working?
Yelli kelsa maad beku?
Where do you want to work?
Yenu beku?
What do you want?
Yellinda barthidira?
Where are you coming from?
Nanna hesaru rhea
My name is Rhea
Naanu engineering od tidini
I study engineering
Banashankari ge hog beku
I want to go to Banshankari
Ondu lota neeru beku
I want a glass of water
Bombay indha bandidini
I come from Bombay




